hat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20unfurling%20and%20hoisting%20the%20flag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20crucial%20distinction%20lies%20in%20the%20placement%20of%20the%20flag%20during%20these%20ceremonies.%20The%20process%20of%20unfurling%20involves%20unveiling%20a%20folded%20or%20rolled-up%20flag%20attached%20to%20a%20rope%20while%20hoisting%20is%20the%20act%20of%20raising%20a%20flag%20up%20a%20pole%20using%20a%20halyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20the%20Indian%20flag%20unfurled%20on%20Republic%20Day%20but%20hoisted%20on%20Independence%20Day%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20Republic%20Day%2C%20the%20flag%20is%20unfurled%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20closed%20and%20tied%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20flagpole.%20The%20flag%20is%20unfolded%20by%20the%20President%20without%20pulling%20it%20up.%20Republic%20Day%20marks%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20in%201950.%20The%20flag%20is%20unfurled%20as%20a%20symbolic%20gesture%20to%20renew%20the%20commitment%20to%20the%20principles%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20highlighting%20the%20shift%20from%20colonial%20rule%20to%20a%20sovereign%2C%20democratic%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20different%20from%20Independence%20Day%2C%20where%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20hoists%20the%20flag%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20pole.%20Flag%20hoisting%20during%20Independence%20Day%20often%20includes%20a%20ceremonial%20event%20with%20a%20military%20or%20civilian%20honour%20guard%20raising%20the%20flag%20while%20the%20national%20anthem%20is%20played.%20The%20hoisting%20on%20Independence%20Day%20symbolises%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20new%20nation%2C%20patriotism%2C%20and%20freedom%20from%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBoth%20ceremonies%2C%20although%20differing%20in%20execution%2C%20hold%20immense%20significance%20in%20commemorating%20India's%20journey%20toward%20freedom%20and%20its%20evolution%20as%20a%20sovereign%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706208660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fn7vsgr3g_republic-day-parade-2024_625x300_26_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepublic-day-2024-difference-between-unfurling-and-hoisting-national-flag-4929828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20India%20prepares%20to%20celebrate%20Republic%20Day%2C%20this%20year%20holds%20special%20significance%2C%20marking%2075%20years%20since%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepublic-day-2024-difference-between-unfurling-and-hoisting-national-flag-4929828%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepublic-day-2024-difference-between-unfurling-and-hoisting-national-flag-4929828%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepublic-day-2024-difference-between-unfurling-and-hoisting-national-flag-4929828%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20sent%20wages%20soaring%20as%20workers%20grow%20scarce%20and%20private%20business%20competes%20with%20the%20military%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Putin%20navy%20military%20russia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b8e4ebc8ea82ff4248b4cb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussia%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20record%202.3%20million%20worker%20shortage.%3Cp%3ESputnik%2FMikhail%20Klementyev%2FKremlin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWages%20in%20Russia%20are%20soaring%20thanks%20to%20the%20nation's%20war%20with%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECompensation%20across%20private%20industries%20rose%20as%20much%20as%2020%25%20last%20year%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMoscow%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20severe%20worker%20shortage%2C%20with%20a%20record%202.3%20million%20workers%20needed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20severe%20shortage%20of%20workers%20in%20Russia%20means%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20beefing%20up%20compensation%20to%20attract%20talent%20%E2%80%94%20and%20competing%20directly%20with%20the%20military%20for%20manpower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%2C%20machine%20operators%2C%20drivers%2C%20welders%2C%20and%20similar%20types%20of%20workers%20can%20now%20find%20equivalent%20or%20even%20better%20pay%20working%20for%20private%20companies%20than%20for%20the%20Russian%20government.%20Wages%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20rose%20between%208%25-20%25%20in%20Russia%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Russian%20recruitment%20agency%20Superjob%20cited%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnnbloomberg.ca%2Frussia-s-war-fuels-a-wage-spiral-that-threatens-army-recruitment-1.2025751%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20puts%20Russia's%20military%20in%20a%20tough%20position%20competing%20with%20the%20private%20sector.%20Salaries%20for%20military%20servicemen%20rose%2010.5%25%20last%20summer%2C%20far%20short%20of%20the%20heftiest%20private%20sector%20pay%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20war%20effort%2C%20Russia%20mostly%20relies%20on%20volunteers%20to%20fight%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20Junior%20ranking%20positions%20in%20Russia's%20army%20make%20around%20210%2C000%20rubles%2C%20or%20%242%2C367%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20nearly%20three%20times%20the%20national%20average%20salary%20in%20Russia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UK%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20%E2%80%94%20though%20higher%20wages%20elsewhere%20seem%20to%20be%20making%20military%20pay%20less%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20highly%20likely%20that%20the%20salary%20and%20additional%20benefits%20are%20a%20strong%20incentive%20for%20personnel%20to%20join%20up%2C%20especially%20to%20those%20from%20the%20poorer%20areas%20of%20Russia.%20However%20Russia%20is%20still%20unlikely%20to%20meet%20its%20targets%20for%20recruiting%20volunteers%20to%20the%20ranks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%20said%20in%20an%20August%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDefenceHQ%2Fstatus%2F1696394754865455170%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20December%2C%20Moscow%20needed%20a%20record%202.3%20million%20workers%20to%20fill%20available%20jobs%20in%20the%20country%2C%20though%20the%20nation's%20unemployment%20rate%20hovered%20near%20a%20historic%20low%20of%202.9%25%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Russian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shortage%20of%20labor%20is%20so%20bad%2C%20Russia%20has%20even%20returned%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-economy-worker-shortage-prison-labor-ukraine-war-putin-kremlin-2023-10%5C%22%3ESoviet%20practice%20of%20using%20prison%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prop%20up%20ailing%20industries.%20Moscow%20pulled%20an%20estimated%2019.1%20billion%20rubles%2C%20or%20%24204%20million%20from%20forced%20prison%20labor%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Moscow%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-worker-shortage-ukraine-war-military-wages-unemployment-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706208283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b8e525604f16230008b58b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-worker-shortage-ukraine-war-military-wages-unemployment-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Moscow%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20severe%20worker%20shortage%2C%20with%20a%20record%202.3%20million%20workers%20needed%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023.