20Countess%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20People's%20Rally%20to%20Cancel%20Student%20Debt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20group%20of%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20called%20on%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20expand%20its%20second%20student-debt%20relief%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20department's%20proposal%20doesn't%20include%20a%20category%20for%20borrowers%20with%20hardship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawmakers%20want%20another%20negotiation%20session%20to%20address%20those%20borrowers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20time%20for%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20to%20consider%20more%20student-loan%20borrowers%20for%20its%20second%20debt%20relief%20plan%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Democrats%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%2038%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Sens.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%2C%20Chuck%20Schumer%2C%20and%20Bernie%20Sanders%20%E2%80%94%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20regarding%20the%20department's%20process%20to%20get%20more%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20to%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%20at%20broad%20relief%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20announced%20it%20would%20pursue%20a%20new%20route%20for%20relief%20using%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965.%20That%20law%20requires%20the%20administration%20to%20undergo%20a%20series%20of%20negotiation%20sessions%20with%20stakeholders%20to%20craft%20the%20final%20rule%20for%20relief%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-what-is-next-biden-debt-cancellation-relief-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20department%20concluded%20its%20third%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20final%20%E2%80%94%20session%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20of%20the%20negotiators%20and%20advocates%20have%20previously%20pushed%20for%20the%20department%20to%20add%20a%20fourth%20negotiation%20session%20to%20consider%20including%20more%20borrowers%20experiencing%20financial%20hardship%20in%20its%20proposal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%2C%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20are%20asking%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20appreciate%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Department%20and%20the%20negotiating%20committee%2C%20we%20are%20concerned%20that%2C%20without%20full%20consideration%20of%20cancellation%20targeted%20toward%20borrowers%20facing%20financial%20hardship%2C%20the%20rule%20will%20not%20provide%20adequate%20debt%20relief%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawmakers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20issue%20concerns%20the%20groups%20of%20borrowers%20the%20Education%20Department%20proposed%20to%20include%20in%20its%20relief.%20It%20outlined%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-will-qualify-second-attempt-biden-education-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20groups%20of%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20third%20negotiation%20session%20that%20could%20qualify%20for%20relief%2C%20including%20those%20who%20have%20paid%20more%20than%20their%20original%20balances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20some%20push%20from%20the%20negotiators%2C%20the%20department%20did%20not%20consider%20a%20category%20for%20borrowers%20experiencing%20hardship.%20The%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20wrote%20in%20their%20letter%20that%20hardship%20could%20include%20whether%20a%20borrower%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20didn't%20complete%20their%20degree%2C%20or%20holds%20parent%20PLUS%20loans%20while%20still%20repaying%20their%20own%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20has%20not%20yet%20indicated%20whether%20it%20will%20add%20a%20fourth%20session.%20In%20response%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-qualifies-student-loan-forgiveness-borrowers-with-hardship-advocacy-groups-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecall%20from%20advocates%20last%20week%20urging%20the%20department%20to%20do%20so%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20was%20reviewing%20the%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department's%20priority%20is%20to%20support%20students%20and%20borrowers%2C%20and%20is%20moving%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20to%20provide%20student%20debt%20relief%20to%20as%20many%20borrowers%20as%20possible%2C%20including%20through%20the%20regulatory%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20adding%20an%20additional%20session%20could%20slow%20the%20process%20down%20to%20implement%20the%20final%20rule%20for%20debt%20relief%2C%20lawmakers%20and%20advocates%20said%20the%20department%20should%20attempt%20to%20make%20the%20rule%20as%20broad%20as%20possible%20to%20expand%20the%20number%20of%20borrowers%20that%20can%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Biden%20Administration%20must%20continue%20to%20use%20its%20authority%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20promises%20made%20to%20student%20loan%20borrowers%20and%20hold%20a%20fourth%20negotiated%20rulemaking%20session%2C%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%20to%20complete%20discussion%20of%20hardship-based%20relief%E2%80%94and%20once%20complete%2C%20swiftly%20propose%20and%20implement%20debt%20relief%20for%20millions%20of%20hard-working%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Democrats%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-more-borrowers-included-hardship-warren-sanders-schumer-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%