%20Temple%20Existed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20has%20revealed%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20temple%2C%20complete%20with%2034%20inscriptions%20in%20various%20languages%2C%20which%20was%20remodelled%20into%20a%20mosque%2C%20the%20lawyer%20of%20the%20women%C2%A0%20petitioners%20told%20the%20media%20today%20after%20receiving%20a%20hard%20copy%20of%20the%20survey%20report.%20The%20Varanasi%20district%20judge%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20make%20the%20report%20public%20immediately%20or%20distribute%20soft%20copies%20to%20avoid%20any%20distortion%20and%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20on%20social%20media%20in%20view%20of%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGyanvapi%20is%20one%20of%20the%20several%20temple-mosque%20disputes%20that%20mushroomed%20in%20the%20country%20after%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Janambhoomi%20issue.%20The%20ASI%20report%20-%20submitted%20a%20month%20ago%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20--%20was%20distributed%20days%20after%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20at%20a%20mega%20programme%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20this%20evening%2C%20Vishnu%20Jain%2C%20the%20lawyer%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20read%20excerpts%20from%20the%20report%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%20The%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20during%20its%20survey%2C%20found%20a%20%26quot%3Bpre-existing%20structure%20and%20a%20well%20next%20to%20the%20corridor%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BCentral%20chamber%20and%20the%20main%20entrance%20have%20a%20pre-existing%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%2C%20in%20its%20survey%2C%20%26quot%3BStudied%20the%20pillars%20and%20plasters%20and%20said%20all%20were%20part%20of%20the%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jain%2C%20while%20reading%20out%20the%20ASI%20report.%20%26quot%3B34%20inscriptions%20of%20Hindu%20temple%20were%20found%20and%20the%20inscriptions%20are%20in%20Devnagri%2C%20Granth%2C%20Telugu%20and%20Kannada.%20Names%20of%20deities%20Janaradana%2C%20Rudra%20and%20Umeshwara%20are%20found%20in%20inscriptions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20from%20the%20report%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTerms%20such%20as%20Maha%20Mukti%20Mandap%20are%20mentioned%20in%20inscriptions...%20pillars%20from%20an%20earlier%20temple%20were%20reused%20while%20making%20cellars.%26quot%3B%C2%A0The%20petitioners'%20lawyer%20has%20said%20that%20they%20will%20ask%20for%20an%20ASI%20survey%20of%20Wazukhana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20had%20been%20surveying%20since%20August%204%20last%20year%20on%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20premises.%20It%20has%20only%20left%20out%20the%20Wazukhana%20area%2C%20which%20was%20sealed%20by%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20crucial%20to%20the%20decision%20in%20the%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Hindu%20side%20contends%20the%20mosque%20has%20been%20built%20over%20a%20temple%20and%20demands%20the%20right%20to%20worship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706204460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Fcdm93fug_gyanvapi-mosque-pti-650_650x400_23_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawyer-for-petitioners-in-gyanvapi-case-holds-press-conference-with-report-by-archaeological-survey-of-india-4931633%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20has%20revealed%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20temple%2C%20complete%20with%2034%20inscriptions%20in%20various%20languages%2C%20which%20was%20remodelled%20into%20a%20mosque%2C%20the%20lawyer%20of%20the%20women%20petitioners%20told%20the%20media%20today%20after%20receiving%20a%20hard%20copy%20of%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawyer-for-petitioners-in-gyanvapi-case-holds-press-conference-with-report-by-archaeolo