%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fflipkart-may-let-go-of-1-000-employees-swiggy-lays-off-350-400-people-124012501144_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fflipkart-may-let-go-of-1-000-employees-swiggy-lays-off-350-400-people-124012501144_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fflipkart-may-let-go-of-1-000-employees-swiggy-lays-off-350-400-people-124012501144_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20Civil%20Society%20to%20Put%20in%20Place%20an%20Independent%20Expert%20Panel%20to%20Monitor%202024%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09193848%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.38.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Citizens%E2%80%99%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20and%20technocrat%20Sam%20Pitroda%20Thursday%20said%20a%20group%20will%20be%20put%20in%20place%20to%20monitor%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20group%20will%20comprise%20seven%20members%20including%20four%20from%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20from%20Chicago%2C%20Pitroda%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20modalities%20are%20being%20worked%20out%20and%20this%20group%20will%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20the%20elections.%20The%20citizens%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20present%20system%20of%20conducting%20elections%20using%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%20This%20group%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20issues%20other%20than%20EVMs%2C%20such%20as%20those%20raised%20by%20the%20CCE%20including%20flaws%20in%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20and%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20way%20to%20conduct%20elections%20is%20paper%20ballots%20if%20the%20trust%20deficit%20is%20to%20be%20bridged%2C%20Pitroda%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20civil%20society%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20petitioning%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20either%20go%20back%20to%20paper%20ballots%20or%20to%20do%20a%20100%25%20count%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20about%20pushing%20for%20digital%20India.%20It%20is%20about%20going%20back%20to%20the%20fundamentals%2C%20going%20back%20to%20paper.%20And%20the%202024%20election%20will%20decide%20the%20destiny%20of%20the%20nation%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come.%20The%20voter%20no%20longer%20knows%20whom%20to%20trust%20where%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20are%20concerned.%20We%20have%20to%20convince%20the%20voter%2C%20not%20the%20ECI%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20The%20ECI%20has%20been%20steadfast%20in%20its%20refusal%20to%20address%20the%20concerns%20of%20civil%20society%20even%20though%20the%20concerns%20raised%20in%20the%20CCE%20report%20are%20alarming%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20questions%20whether%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20would%20be%20urged%20to%20add%20this%20demand%20of%20paper%20ballots%20to%20their%20manifestos%2C%20Pitroda%2C%20who%20said%20he%20is%20speaking%20as%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20and%20not%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CManifestos%20come%20in%20the%20end.%20This%20problem%20has%20to%20be%20solved%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20opposition%20is%20not%20speaking%20in%20one%20voice%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20EVMs%20Pitroda%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20advice%20to%20the%20opposition%20is%20to%20wake%20up.%20But%20it%20is%20for%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20answer%20as%20to%20how%20they%20intend%20to%20take%20up%20an%20issue%20that%20affects%20them%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCE%20convenor%20M.G.%20Devasahayam%20said%20various%20citizens%E2%80%99%20groups%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20draw%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20concerns%20about%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20elections%20but%20to%20little%20avail.%20He%20said%20the%20CCE%20report%20put%20together%20by%20global%20experts%20in%20the%20fields%20of%20computer%20science%20and%20electronics%20has%20clearly%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20absence%20of%20end-to-end%20verifiability%20of%20the%20voting%20process%20the%20present%20system%20is%20unfit%20for%20democratic%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevasahayam%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20practice%2C%20there%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20100%25%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips.%20The%20system%20should%20be%20software%20and%20hardware-independent%20to%20be%20verifiable%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20German%20Supreme%20Court%20threw%20out%20EVMs%20and%20declared%20unconstitutional%20any%20electoral%20process%20that%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20democracy%20and%20end-to-end%20verifiability%20meaning%20the%20voter%20should%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20verify%20her%20vote%20has%20been%20cast%20as%20intended%20and%20recorded%20as%20cast.%20That%20is%20not%20happening%20in%20the%20present%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20critics%20who%20say%20paper%20ballots%20are%20a%20long%20tedious%20process%20of%20counting%2C%20Devashayam%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20takes%20weeks%2C%20if%20not%20months%20to%20conduct%20an%20election.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20counting%20process%2C%20they%20are%20in%20a%20tearing%20hurry%20and%20want%20to%20get%20over%20the%20counting%20process%20in%20a%20hurry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Pitroda%20and%20Devashayam%20said%20the%20issue%20is%20no%20longer%20about%20whether%20the%20system%20can%20be%20hacked%20or%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20or%20the%20software%20used.%20The%20issue%2C%20they%20said%2C%20is%20to%20revive%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20people%20in%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706203528000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire