destroy%20larger%2C%20more%20expensive%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20While%20the%20proliferation%20of%20drones%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20subcontinent%2C%20we%20have%20a%20plan%20to%20boost%20our%20air%20defence%20capabilities%20because%20now%20we%20have%20a%20huge%20spectrum%20of%20threats%2C%20starting%20from%20small%20drones%20to%20hypersonic%20weapons.%20So%20the%20air%20defence%20network%20and%20capabilities%20need%20to%20be%20strengthened%20in%20equal%20measure%2C%26quot%3B%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20briefly%20explained%20the%20process%20that%20India%20has%20been%20following%20in%20developing%20drones%20of%20all%20types%2C%20from%20basic%20to%20complex%20machines%2C%20involving%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20small%20private%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BMehar%20Baba%20Competition%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20Indian%20start-ups%20to%20develop%20a%20swarm%20drone-based%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20astonishing%20results%20from%20the%20Mehar%20Baba%20Competition%2C%20and%20incubated%20many%20small%20firms.%20Many%20small%20industries%20that%20started%20making%20drones%20in%20swarms%20have%20been%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20requirements%20that%20we%20had%20projected%20at%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20industry%20is%20really%20galloping%20within%20our%20country%2C%20and%20most%20of%20it%20is%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20and%20small%20scale%2C%20and%20we%20encourage%20all%20of%20them%20to%20come%20up%20with%20their%20ideas%20and%20see%20how%20we%20can%20implement%20them%20in%20our%20broader%20operational%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20bigger%20platforms%20that%20can%20fly%20high%20and%20have%20long%20endurance%2C%20we%20are%20collaborating%20with%20other%20industries%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20a%20long-term%20plan%20for%20homegrown%20capability%20in%20this%20field.%20So%20the%20whole%20drone%20ecosystem%20is%20being%20supported%20and%20encouraged%20by%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20particularly%20by%20the%20IAF%2C%26quot%3B%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706199960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fo6romc68_air-chief-marshal-vr-choudhary_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrones-becoming-weapon-of-choice-air-chief-marshal-vr-choudhary-ndtv-exclusive-interview-4931528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drones%20are%20becoming%20the%20weapon%20of%20choice%20for%20state%20and%20non-state%20actors%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20VR%20Choudhary%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrones-becoming-weapon-of-choice-air-chief-marshal-vr-choudhary-ndtv-exclusive-interview-4931528%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrones-becoming-weapon-of-choice-air-chief-marshal-vr-choudhary-ndtv-exclusive-interview-4931528%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrones-becoming-weapon-of-choice-air-chief-marshal-vr-choudhary-ndtv-exclusive-interview-4931528%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20To%20Swap%20Alliances%20Again%3F%20May%20Share%20Stage%20With%20PM%20In%20Bihar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20appears%20to%20be%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20unravelling%20as%20a%20third%20key%20leader%2C%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20appears%20likely%20to%20walk%20out.%20Sources%20said%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20in%20a%20last-minute%20U-turn%2C%20will%20partner%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20days%2C%20two%20key%20leaders%20--%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20--%20have%20all%20but%20cut%20ties%20with%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20ruling%20out%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20saying%20they%20would%20go%20solo%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20--%20who%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20may%20even%20share%20stage%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20his%20February%204%20rally%20in%20Bettiah%20--%20has%20called%20all%20his%20MLAs%20to%20Patna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20party%20now%20has%20two%20options%20--%20dissolve%20the%20assembly%20and%20hold%20assembly%20elections%20alongside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Else%20allow%20Mr%20Kumar%20to%20continue%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20--%20which%20is%20being%20greatly%20resisted%20the%20party's%20local%20leaders.%20It%20is%20now%20willing%20to%20wait%20and%20watch%20as%20the%20events%20unfold%20in%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%20243-member%20Bihar%20assembly%20is%20122.%20The%20RJD%20has%2079%20seats.%20Mr%20Kumar%20can%20form%20government%20with%2082%20seats%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%2045%20of%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20United.%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20has%2079%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20political%20tumult%2C%20the%20Bihar%20Governor%2C%20who%20was%20to%20travel%20to%20Goa%20tomorrow%20evening%2C%20has%20cancelled%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20even%20though%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20skeptical%20about%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20return%2C%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20party%20has%20made%20up%20its%20mind%20and%20issued%20a%20gag%20order%20for%20the%20state%20unit.%20State%20leaders%20have%20been%20categorically%20told%20not%20to%20badmouth%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20chief%C2%A0%20Samrat%20Chaudhary%20has%20been%20called%20to%20Delhi.%20He%20and%20senior%20Bihar%20leader%20Sushil%20Modi%20are%20likely%20to%20meet%20party%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20and%20the%20BJP's%20chief%20strategist%20Amit%20Shah%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%2072%2C%20this%20would%20be%20the%20fifth%20change%20of%20camp.%20Since%202013%2C%20he%20has%20been%20swinging%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20mahagathbandhan%2C%20all%20the%20while%20keeping%20his%20job%20in%20the%20state%20intact.%20He%20switched%20sides%20last%20in%202022%2C%20just%20three%20years%20after%20he%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Grand%20Alliance%20and%20joined%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signs%20have%20all%20been%20there%20over%20the%20last%20weeks%2C%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20sharp%20comments%20on%20dynastic%20politics%20and%20the%20subsequent%20retort%20from%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20daughter%20on%20social%20media%2C%20despite%20later%20deletion%2C%20expanding%20the%20rift.%20Mr%20Kumar's%20comments%20were%20seen%20as%20a%20snub%20to%20ally%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20his%20son%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20even%20though%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Party%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%2C%20denied%20it%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Mr%20Kumar's%20lack%20of%20response%20to%20the%20Congress%20invitation%20for%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20put%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20his%20appearance%20and%20raised%20speculation%20about%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20Opposition%20front.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20been%20upset%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20in%20INDIA%20bloc's%20poll%20preparations%20and%20being%20passed%20over%20as%20a%20possible%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate.%20The%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20had%20been%20a%20further%20aggravation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20build-up%20to%20the%20change%20of%20camp%20had%20started%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20sacking%20Lallan%20Singh%20and%20returning%20as%20the%20JDU%