lf%20played%20a%20not%20insignificant%20role%20in%20India's%20charge%20on%20the%20day%2C%20plucking%20the%20wickets%20of%20Jonny%20Bairstow%20and%20Ben%20Foakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year-old%20said%20he%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20complement%20senior%20partners%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%20seniors%20Ash%20and%20Jaddu%20bhai.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20control%20the%20game%20from%20my%20end%20as%20they%20were%20bowling%20in%20partnership.%20They%20were%20taking%20wickets%2C%20so%2C%20I%20was%20not%20thinking%20about%20taking%20wickets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20if%20you%20are%20playing%20three%20spinners%20then%20one%20of%20them%20will%20get%20a%20lesser%20number%20of%20overs.%20They%20were%20also%20telling%20me%20what%20was%20happening%20on%20the%20wicket%20and%20what%20I%20should%20do.%20It%20is%20a%20privilege%20to%20bowl%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Axar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20bowler%20was%20particularly%20chuffed%20about%20the%20dismissal%20of%20Bairstow%20after%20castling%20him%20with%20a%20gem%20of%20a%20delivery%20that%20was%20bowled%20from%20wide%20of%20the%20crease%2C%20hitting%20the%20stumps%20with%20the%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20delivery%20really%20came%20off%20well.%20We%20were%20talking%20if%20it%20turns%20from%20there%20then%20it%20would%20be%20great%20because%20the%20odd%20ball%20was%20turning.%20Bairstow%20took%20stance%20on%20the%20fourth%20wicket%20to%20avoid%20the%20lbw.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20bowling%20at%20the%20stumps%20because%20he%20did%20cut%20a%20few%20shots%20close%20to%20the%20stumps.%20That%20was%20the%20plan%20and%20the%20one%20that%20turned%20from%20there%20was%20good%20and%20you%20would%20have%20seen%20my%20celebration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20attempt%20to%20negate%20Indian%20spinners%2C%20t