ng%3EMarket%20veteran%20Ed%20Yardeni%20is%20growing%20increasingly%20worried%20about%20a%20stock%20market%20meltup.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EYardeni%20said%20sentiment%20measures%20like%20the%20put-to-call%20ratio%20are%20flashing%20contrarian%20bearish%20signals.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20meltups%20is%20that%20they%20do%20need%20to%20meltdown%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMarket%20veteran%20Ed%20Yardeni%20is%20growing%20increasingly%20worried%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-melt-up-1990s-record-highs-interest-rate-cuts-2024-1%5C%22%3Ea%20potential%20stock%20market%20meltup%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20keeps%20hitting%20new%20record%20highs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYardeni%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20bulls%20on%20Wall%20Street%20since%20the%20stock%20market%20bottomed%20in%20October%202022%2C%20and%20his%202024%20and%202025%20year-end%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20price%20targets%20of%205%2C400%20and%206%2C000%2C%20respectively%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2F2024-stock-market-investment-outlooks-wall-street-prediction-roundup-sp500-2023-11%5C%22%3Eare%20some%20of%20the%20highest%20among%20market%20strategists.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20stock%20market's%20surge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-news-sp500-record-high-bull-market-rally-earnings-2024-1%5C%22%3Eto%20consecutive%20record%20highs%20in%20the%20past%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20led%20Yardeni%20to%20offer%20some%20cautious%20comments%2C%20as%20the%20strategist%20worries%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20rally%20has%20gone%20too%20far%20too%20fast%20and%20could%20ultimately%20suffer%20the%20type%20of%20meltup%20and%20meltdown%20that%20happened%20during%20the%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20meltups%20is%20that%20they%20do%20need%20to%20meltdown%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20note%20to%20clients%2C%20Yardeni%20highlighted%20short-term%20sentiment%20measures%20that%20suggest%20there%20is%20reason%20for%20caution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bull%2FBear%20ratios%2C%20derived%20from%20the%20Investors%20Intelligence%20and%20AAII%20investment%20sentiment%20surveys%2C%20have%20hit%20elevated%20levels%20recently.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20put-to-call%20ratio%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20amount%20of%20protection%20investors%20are%20buying%20via%20options%20contracts%2C%20has%20hit%20relatively%20low%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20contrarian%20perspective%2C%20that's%20bearish%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20reason%20why%20stocks%20have%20moved%20so%20much%20higher%20in%20recent%20weeks%20and%20months%2C%20according%20to%20Yardeni.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20economy%20and%20jobs%20market%20remains%20resilient%20and%20on%20strong%20footing%2C%20and%20that%20inflation%20has%20come%20down%20considerably.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20reinforced%20by%20the%20fourth-quarter%20GDP%20release%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-outlook-economy-gdp-fourth-quarter-of-2023-2024-1%5C%22%3Ewhich%20showed%20economic%20growth%20of%203.3%25%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20well%20ahead%20of%20economist%20expectations%20for%20growth%20of%202.0%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20strong%20data%20also%20plays%20into%20one%20of%20Yardeni's%20biggest%20worries%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-slowdown-interest-rates-outlook-federal-reserve-cuts-next-year-2023-11%5C%22%3Ethe%20potential%20for%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20to%20lower%20interest%20rates%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20could%20exacerbate%20a%20meltup%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20what%20could%20happen%20if%20the%20Fed%20actually%20starts%20lowering%20interest%20rates.%20That's%20what%20I%20am%20concerned%20about%20is%20that%20that%20could%20spark%20a%20meltup%20in%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Yardeni%2C%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20are%20akin%20to%20the%20Fed%20pouring%20gasoline%20on%20the%20stock%20market%20rally%2C%20and%20it%20could%20fuel%20further%20asset%20price%20inflation%20and%20even%20drive%20a%20rebound%20in%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Fed%20would%20be%20making%20a%20mistake%20to%20lower%20interest%20rates.%20I%20think%20Powell%20is%20going%20to%20start%20pushing%20back%20against%20%5Bthat%5D.%20He's%20very%20aware%20of%20market%20forces%20and%20if%20the%20stock%20market%20just%20keeps%20going%20up%2C%20it%20creates%20a%20positive%20wealth%20effect%20and%20then%20that%20creates%20the%20potential%20for%20inflation%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-meltup-outlook-fed-interest-rates-inflation-ed-yardeni-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706199258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b26f6843bb77284ba089cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-meltup-outlook-fed-interest-rates-inflation-ed-yardeni-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20meltups%20is%20that%20they%20do%20need%20to%20meltdown%2C%26quot%3B%20market%20veteran%20Ed%20Yardeni%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.business