mu%20said%20in%20the%20televised%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20acknowledged%20the%20contribution%20to%20society%20by%20former%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Karpoori%20Thakur%2C%20and%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20temple%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ayodhya%20as%20a%20historic%20and%20an%20immensely%20significant%20moment%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20pay%20my%20tribute%20to%20Karpoori%20ji%20for%20enriching%20public%20life%20with%20his%20contribution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarpoori%20Thakur%2C%20the%20two-term%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20died%20in%201988%2C%20has%20been%20named%20for%20the%20country's%20highest%20civilian%20award%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20his%20contribution%20to%20uplifting%20the%20poor%20and%20backward%20classes.%20During%20his%20political%20career%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20was%20considered%20the%20guiding%20light%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20politics%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKarpoori%20ji%20belonged%20to%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20dedicated%20his%20life%20for%20their%20welfare%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Murmur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20pay%20my%20tribute%20to%20Karpoori%20Ji%20for%20enriching%20public%20life%20through%20his%20contributions.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRebJqrnl8k%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRebJqrnl8k%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20President%20of%20India%20(%40rashtrapatibhvn)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frashtrapatibhvn%2Fstatus%2F1750518366417367395%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20announcement%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20villagers%20of%20the%20'Karpoori%20gram'%20in%20Bihar's%20Samastipur%20district%20had%20met%20the%20family%20members%20of%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20and%20his%20elder%20son%20Ramnath%20Thakur%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20or%20JD(U).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20JD(U)%20leader%20Neeraj%20Kumar%20had%20said%20Nitish%20Kumar%20had%20been%20requesting%20the%20Centre%20to%20honour%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna.%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20it%20came%20late%2C%20it%20is%20a%20welcome%20decision%20and%20will%20inspire%20the%20youth%20to%20take%20up%20his%20ideals%2C%26quot%3B%20Neeraj%20Kumar%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20all%20indication%20point%20towards%20him%20leaving%20the%20newly%20formed%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA.%20The%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20will%20not%20join%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20when%20it%20enters%20the%20state%20on%20January%2030%2C%20sources%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20is%2C%20however%2C%20likely%20to%20share%20the%20stage%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20visits%20Bihar%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20decision%20to%20not%20walk%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20whose%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20or%20JD(U)%2C%20which%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20in%20the%20ruling%20Bihar%20government%2C%20has%20given%20a%20subtle%20message%20that%20all%20is%20not%20well%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706195700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F6hegqlug_president-droupadi-murmu_625x300_08_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpresident-droupadi-murmu-addresses-nation-day-before-indias-75th-republic-day-4930675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20today%20addressed%20the%20nation%20on%20the%20e