h%20India.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20we%20thought%2C%20Oh%2C%20here%20we%20go.%20Next%20ball.%20Then%20we%20get%20the%20ball%20to%20bounce.%20Then%20we%20get%20the%20ball%20to%20spin.%20Then%20another%20one%20bounces.%20We%20just%20didn't%20see%20that%20with%20the%20England%20spinners%2C%26quot%3B%20Pietersen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20was%20batting%20on%20a%2070-ball%2076%20while%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20unbeaten%20on%2014%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day's%20play%2C%20as%20India%20trailed%20by%20127%20runs%20after%20losing%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20(24).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20captain%20Ben%20Stokes%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visitors%20were%20off%20to%20a%20decant%20start%20with%20openers%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Zak%20Crawley%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112318-zak-crawley-playerprofile%5C%22%3EZak%20Crawley%3C%2Fa%3E%20(20)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Duckett%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63527-ben-matthew-duckett-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Duckett%3C%2Fa%3E%20(35)%20adding%2055%20runs%20at%20a%20fairly%20good%20pace%20before%20Ravichandran%C2%A0Ashwin%C2%A0gave%20India%20their%20first%20breakthrough%20by%20having%20Duckett%20trapped%20in%20front%20of%20the%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStokes%20top-scored%20with%2070%20off%2088%20balls%20and%20was%20the%20last%20English%20wicket%20to%20fall%2C%20bowled%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3