raging%20religious%20feelings%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20around%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20that%20took%20place%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incidents%20range%20from%20inflammatory%20posts%20and%20offensive%20sloganeering%20to%20installing%20Hindu%20saffron%20flags%20atop%20mosques%20during%20shobha%20yatra%20or%20insulting%20them.%20Three%20incidents%20each%20were%20reported%20from%20Kanpur%2C%20and%20Shahjahanpur%20districts%20in%20central%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20other%20incidents%20were%20reported%20in%20Agra%2C%20Azamgarh%2C%20Kushinagar%2C%20and%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%2C%20a%20mob%20of%20right-wing%20hooligans%20forcibly%20tried%20to%20enter%20a%20mosque%20in%20the%20Mehdawal%20area%20during%20a%20shobha%20yatra%20on%20January%2022.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20posted%20by%20the%20miscreants%20themselves%2C%20showed%20a%20large%20group%20of%20men%20creating%20a%20ruckus%20in%20front%20of%20a%20mosque%2C%20dancing%20in%20front%20of%20its%20gate%20while%20waiving%20tall%20saffron%20flags.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBharat%20ka%20baccha%20bachha%20jai%20jai%20shri%20ram%20bolega.%20Har%20ghar%20mein%20ek%20hi%20naam%2C%20ek%20hi%20naara%20gunjega%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20song%20featured%20in%20the%20video%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20they%20arrested%20five%20persons%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident.%20They%20were%20identified%20as%20Ganesh%20Prajapati%2C%20Siddhant%20Jaiswal%2C%20Ashok%20Kumar%2C%20Anil%2C%20and%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kushinagar%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%2010%20Muslim%20men%20and%20other%20unidentified%20persons%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20pelting%20stones%20and%20bricks%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3Edwaj%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(shobha%20yatra)%20that%20was%20taken%20out%20in%20the%20Barwa%20Bazar%20area%20village%20in%20Kasia.%20The%20complainant%20Guddu%20Madeshia%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20village%20Pradhan%2C%20also%20alleged%20that%20when%20the%20shobha%20yatra%20of%20some%20children%20was%20peacefully%20crossing%20the%20Bazar%20tola%20locality%2C%20Muslim%20youth%20objected%20to%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogans%20and%20attacked%20those%20participating%20in%20the%20yatra%20with%20lathis%20while%20also%20abusing%20them.%20Three%20motorbikes%20were%20damaged%20and%20four%20to%20five%20children%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20alleged%20Madeshia%20in%20his%20police%20complaint%2C%20seen%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20persons%20were%20identified%20as%20Shaukat%2C%20Sageer%2C%20Rehan%20Ansari%2C%20Javed%20Ansari%2C%20Ajmal%2C%20Wazeem%2C%20Maulvi%20Arif%20Raza%20Siddiqui%2C%20Naushad%2C%20Munsaf%20and%20Ishtaqar.%20They%20were%20booked%20under%20Sections%20147%20(rioting)%2C%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20336%20(rash%20act%20endangering%20life)%2C%20352%20(assault)%2C%20427%20(mischief%20causing%20damage)%20and%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperintendent%20of%20Police%20Kushinagar%20Dhawal%20Jaiswal%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20dispute%20arose%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20over%20the%20bursting%20of%20firecrackers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20report%20of%20stone-pelting%20on%20the%20shobha%20yatra%20is%20false%20and%20baseless%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20officer.%20Jaiswal%20said%20police%20had%20arrested%20four%20persons%20for%20the%20incident%20and%20all%20sides%20of%20the%20matter%20were%20being%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Shajahanpur%2C%20police%20on%20January%2024%20arrested%20seven%20Muslim%20youth%2C%20including%20two%20minors%2C%20for%20allegedly%20desecrating%20saffron%20flags%20put%20up%20on%20the%20street%20in%20the%20Batlaiya%20village%20in%20the%20Katra%20region%20a%20day%20earlier.%20The%20police%20sent%20to%20jail%20five%20persons%2C%20identified%20as%20Mohammad%20Iqbal%2C%20Aman%2C%20Dilpukar%2C%20Mohammad%20Shahid%20and%20Tajju%2C%20while%20two%20minors%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20and%20produced%20before%20a%20juvenile%20court%2C%20said%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Rural)%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Awasthi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20were%20arrested%20on%20the%20charges%20of%20trying%20to%20disrupt%20communal%20harmony%2C%20said%20the%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%20in%20Shahjahanpur%2C%20police%20arrested%20three%20persons%2C%20Ankit%20Katheria%2C%20Rohit%20Joshi%20and%20Rohit%20Saxena%20for%20removing%20a%20flag%20from%20a%20mosque%20in%20the%20Ramchandra%20Mission%20police%20station%20area%20on%20January%2022%20and%20replacing%20it%20with%20a%20saffron%20flag.%20The%20third%20incident%20was%20also%20reported%20in%20the%20same%20area%20where%20a%20man%20Sri%20Dutt%20Mishra%20was%20booked%20and%20arrested%20for%20posting%20a%20video%20of%20him%20online%20showing%20him%20burning%20photos%20of%20Hindu%20deities.%20He%20was%20arrested%20and%20is%20being%20questioned%2C%20said%20Sudhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20additional%20SP%20(City)%2C%20Shahjahanpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Azamgarh%2C%20the%20matter%20got%20tense%20after%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20when%20a%20vehicle%20that%20was%20part%20of%20a%20shobha%20yatra%20on%20January%2022%20in%20Jahanganj%20was%20passing%20through%20a%20locality%20with%20Muslim%20residents.%20Police%20managed%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control%20and%20arrested%20three%20persons%20Mohammad%20Zahid%2C%20Sageer%20and%20Shahnawaz%20and%20recovered%20sticks%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dispute%20arose%20over%20the%20designated%20route%20of%20the%20shobha%20yatra%20following%20which%2040-50%20young%20men%20from%20both%20sides%20confronted%20each%20other%20and%20entered%20a%20dispute%2C%20said%20SP%20City%20Azamgarh%20Shailendra%20Lal%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20police%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20de-escalated%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kanpur%2C%20a%20Hindu%20student%20was%20booked%20for%20making%20offensive%20slogans%20against%20Muslims%20when%20slogans%20for%20Lord%20Ram%20were%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20hostel%20of%20the%20Pranveer%20Singh%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(PSIT)%20in%20Sachendi%20area.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20it%2C%20police%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20under%20Sections%20153%20A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups)%2C%20295A%20(outrage%20religious%20feelings)%20and%20298%20(uttering%20words%20with%20deliberate%20intent%20to%20wound%20religious%20feelings)%20of%20the%20IPC.%20A%20video%20showing%20the%20warden%20of%20the%20hostel%20scolding%20students%20for%20raising%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogans%20in%20the%20campus%20was%20also%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Juhi%20area%20of%20Kanpur%2C%20a%20Muslim%20student%20who%20posted%20photos%20on%20Instagram%20with%20abusive%20songs%20for%20Hindu%20deities%20including%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20was%20booked%20on%20similar%20charges.%20Joint%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20law%20and%20order%20Anand%20Prakash%20Tiwari%20took%20cognisance%20of%20both%20cases%20and%20said%20police%20were%20carrying%20out%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnecessary%20correctional%20measures%E2%80%9D%20and%20would%20ensure%20that%20such%20things%20do%20not%20repeat%20in%20future.%20Tiwari%20said%20police%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20PSIT%20administration%20as%20well%20as%20to%20the%20family%20of%20the%20Muslim%20boy.%20The%20senior%20police%20officer%20appealed%20public%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20repost%2C%20retweet%20or%20recirculate%E2%80%9D%20the%20offensive%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%20in%20Kanpur%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20three%20Muslim%20youth%2C%20Junaid%2C%20Sohail%20and%20Hasnain%20and%20four%20to%20five%20others%20on%20the%20charges%20of%20assaulting%20a%20Hindu%20boy%20on%20January%2023%20after%20threatening%20him%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20ceremony.%20The%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20Babupurwa%20police%20station%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20one%20Seema%20Biswakarma%2C%20who%20underlined%20her%20Hindu%20identity%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20against%20her%20Muslim%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20DCP%20Ankita%20Sharma%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20a%20dispute%20arose%20between%20two%20boys%20over%20the%20stopping%20of%20a%20motorbike.%20There%20was%20no%20law%20and%20order%20problem%20and%20two%20persons%20had%20been%20taken%20into%20custody%20and%20were%20being%20questioned%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20already%2C%20police%20arrested%2011%20persons%20for%20hoisting%20Hindu%20saffron%20flags%20atop%20and%20inside%20a%20Mughal-era%20Mosque%20in%20Agra%20district.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20a%20shobha%20yatra%20taken%20out%20by%20right-wing%20activists%20soon%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20completed%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20at%20the%20site%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20stood%20till%20December%206%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20at%20Tajganj%20police%20station%20on%20January%2023%2C%20the%20caretaker%20of%20the%20Diwan%20ji%20Ki%20Begum%20Shahi%20Masjid%20in%20Billochpura%20alleged%20that%20around%201%2C000-1%2C%20500%20persons%20carrying%20%E2%80%9Clathis%20and%20sticks%E2%80%9D%20forcibly%20barged%20into%20the%20mosque%20at%20around%203%3A30%20pm%20in%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20created%20complete%20chaos%20in%20the%20mosque%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zahir%20Uddin%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Emutawalli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(caretaker)%20of%20the%20mosque.%20In%20his%20police%20complaint%2C%20Zahir%20Uddin%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Canti-social%20elements%E2%80%9D%20hoisted%20saffron%20flags%20on%20the%20minarets%2C%20walls%20and%20in%20the%20inner%20premises%20of%20the%20mosque.%20They%20%E2%80%9Cdesecrated%20the%20mosque%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zahir%20Uddin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20miscreants%20also%20raised%20religious%20slogans%20and%20threatened%20those%20inside%20the%20mosque%2C%20alleged%20the%20caretaker%20of%20the%20mosque.%20They%20were%20%E2%80%9Cunabashedly%20using%20undignified%20language%20for%20the%20other%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20FIR%20said%20quoting%20Zahir%20Uddin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lodged%20against%201%2C000-1%2C500%20unidentified%20persons%20invoked%20Sections%20147%20(rioting)%2C%20148%20(rioting%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20deadly%20weapon)%2C%20452%20(trespass%20after%20preparation%20for%20hurt%20or%20assault)%20and%20505%20(2)%20(statements%20conducing%20to%20public%20mischief)%20of%20the%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706194054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsaffron-flags-atop-mosques-and-insulting-posts-communal-incidents-from-up-around-ram-temple-event%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20at%20least%2010%20communal%20incidents%20were%20reported%20from%20across%20the%20state%2C%20including%20inflammatory%20posts%20and%20offensive%20sloganeering%2C%20in%20and%20around%20the%20day%20of%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsaffron-flags-atop-mosques-and-insulting-posts-communal-incidents-from-up-around-ram-temple-event%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suhana%20shares%20postcard-worthy%20pics%20from%20Paris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706193884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fph