0BJP%20leadership.%20On%20realising%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20go%20ahead%20with%20its%20choice%20anyway%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20ended%20the%20JDU's%2017-year%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20which%20brought%20the%20BJP%20back%20to%20power%20with%20a%20thumping%20majority%2C%20was%20a%20disaster%20for%20Mr%20Kumar.%20JDU%2C%20now%20contesting%20against%20its%20former%20ally%20BJP%2C%20ended%20up%20with%20just%20two%20seats%2C%20a%20drop%20of%2018%20from%20its%202009%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-11%2Flalu-nitish-bihar-pti_650x400_61448044442.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%202015%20Mahagathbandhan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20quit%20has%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20his%20party's%20debacle.%20He%20had%20installed%20Jitam%20Ram%20Manjhi%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20his%20place.%20The%20JDU%20government%20survived%20the%20majority%20test%20in%20the%20Assembly%20with%20the%20support%20of%20RJD%2C%20once%20its%20arch-rival.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20the%20JDU%20contested%20the%20state%20polls%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20RJD%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20scoring%20a%20massive%20victory%20and%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20Mr%20Kumar%20to%20become%20Chief%20Minister%20again.%20However%2C%20this%20victory%20relegated%20Mr%20Kumar%20to%20the%20smaller%20force%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20with%20the%20RJD%20emerging%20as%20the%20big%20brother.%20This%20provided%20a%20perfect%20launchpad%20to%20Lalu%20Prasad%20to%20launch%20his%20son.%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20then%2026%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.