DU's%20diminished%20strength%20in%20the%20Assembly%20meant%20lesser%20autonomy%20for%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20who%20once%20called%20the%20shots%20for%20NDA%20in%20Bihar.%20Differences%20also%20cropped%20up%20over%20issues%20such%20as%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens.%20Things%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%202022%2C%20when%20the%20JDU%20alleged%20a%20BJP%20plot%20to%20split%20the%20party.%20On%20August%209%2C%202022%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20announced%20that%20the%20JDU-BJP%20alliance%20was%20over.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20he%20was%20Chief%20Minister%20again%20with%20support%20from%20the%20RJD%2C%20which%20had%20earlier%20ruled%20out%20any%20tie-up%20with%20Mr%20Kumar%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fm2qhajq8_opposition-meet_625x300_12_April_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20Split%20On%20The%20Way%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20is%20contemplating%20another%20reversal%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20end%20the%20alliance%20with%20RJD.%20If%20this%20happens%2C%20it%20would%20be%20his%20fifth%20flip-flop.%20On%20the%20national%20level%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20putting%20together%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP.%20A%20reversal%20by%20him%20will%20also%20leave%20the%20Opposition%20front%20red-faced.%20Mr%20Kumar's%20refusal%20to%20join%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20which%20is%20about%20to%20enter%20Bihar%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20precursor%20to%20his%20big%20exit.%20The%20BJP%20leadership%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20has%20green-lighted%20Mr%20Kumar's%20return%2C%20but%20state%20leaders%20are%20not%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENitish%20