wire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15175959%2Fmodi-speeches.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20general%20election%20bugle%20is%20about%20to%20be%20sounded%20soon%2C%20the%20nation%20is%20being%20captivated%20by%20a%20blitzkrieg%20of%20Ram%20temple%20mania.%20A%20never%20before%20seen%20advertisement%20campaign%20to%20mark%20the%20consecration%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ftemple-promised-by-bjp-transforms-ayodhya-but-muslims-some-locals-feel-neglected-2815166%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egrand%20temple%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20mosque%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20was%20demolished%20by%20frenzied%20rightwing%20mobs%20in%201992%2C%20now%20hogs%20the%20limelight%20across%20print%2C%20TV%20and%20online%20media.%20Not%20only%20news%20channels%20but%20channels%20of%20all%20hues%20and%20colours%20have%20gone%20full%20Ram%20mode.%20They%20are%20recycling%20anything%20and%20everything%20even%20remotely%20connected%20to%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20epic%20tale%20revered%20by%20a%20section%20of%20Indians.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20being%20touted%20as%20a%20glorious%20achievement%20in%20the%20crown%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9CVishwaguru%E2%80%9D%20(world%20leader)%20by%20his%20obsequious%20supporters%20that%20seem%20abound%20due%20to%20their%20vociferous%20presence%20in%20conspicuous%20media%20spaces.%20Kudos%20to%20the%20event%20management%20skills%20of%20this%20democratically%20elected%20prime%20minister%20of%20India!%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20live%20in%20a%20digital%20era%20where%20such%20outlandish%20event%20management%20is%20all%20it%20takes%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Findia-vishwa-guru-g20-summit-pm-modi-vision-world-8933278%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eself-proclaim%20oneself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CVishwaguru%E2%80%9D%20whether%20you%20consider%20the%20current%20instances%20or%20in%20those%20the%20past%20during%20the%20G-20%20summit%20in%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Independence%20day%20eve%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20It%20behooves%20us%20to%20look%20back%20at%20our%20history%20and%20reflect%20on%20a%20few%20actual%20Vishwagurus%20and%20how%20they%20might%20have%20reacted%20to%20ongoing%20world%20events%20at%20this%20critical%20time%20in%20a%20volatile%20era%20that%20is%20transforming%20rapidly.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoing%20back%20about%203000%20years%2C%20the%20first%20individual%20in%20recorded%20human%20history%20that%20would%20genuinely%20qualify%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%20would%20be%20Siddhartha%20Gautama%2C%20later%20affectionately%20christened%20as%20%E2%80%9CBuddha%E2%80%9D.%20He%20preached%20a%20message%20of%20equality%20and%20love%20in%20a%20world%20around%20him%20that%20was%20full%20of%20segregation%20and%20discrimination.%20No%20wonder%20his%20teachings%20were%20embraced%20in%20every%20country%20east%20of%20India%20and%20a%20religion%20in%20his%20name%20i.e.%20Buddhism%20took%20root.%20Our%20contemporary%20Vishwaguru%20would%20pale%20in%20comparison%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20humility%20and%20practice%20of%20love%20and%20brotherhood%20of%20Siddhartha%E2%80%99s%20scale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-strength-of-indias-religious-traditions-are-spaces-where-people-from-different-religions-intermix%5C%22%3EThe%20Strength%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Religious%20Traditions%20Are%20Spaces%20Where%20People%20From%20Different%20Religions%20Intermix%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20might%20be%20unrealistic%20to%20expect%20such%20qualities%20from%20any%20contemporary%20world%20leader%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20another%20historical%20figure%20from%20India%20who%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20vagaries%20of%20politics%20and%20statecraft%2C%20akin%20to%20present%20day%2C%20more%20than%202300%20years.%20King%20Ashoka%20stood%20tall%20among%20not%20only%20his%20peers%20but%20in%20world%20history%20on%20several%20fronts.%20His%20emphasis%20on%20public%20health%20by%20building%20area%20hospitals%2C%20planting%20shaded%20trees%20along%20highways%20and%20even%20veterinary%20hospitals%20for%20wounded%20horses%20and%20elephants%20is%20unparalleled%20in%20the%20history%20of%20world%20kings.%20Compare%20that%20with%20the%20Nero-esque%20apathy%20displayed%20by%20our%20prime%20minister%20to%20the%20indescribable%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fasia_pacific%2Findia-coronavirus-lockdown-migrant-workers%2F2020%2F03%2F27%2Fa62df166-6f7d-11ea-a156-0048b62cdb51_story.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplight%20of%20our%20very%20own%20daily-wage%20laborers%20(dehumanigingly%20labelled%20%E2%80%9Cmigrant%E2%80%9D%20workers)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cspan%3E%20when%20they%20had%20to%20walk%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20to%20their%20homes%20due%20to%20the%20sudden%20lockdown%20imposed%20by%20the%20shock-and-awe%20specialist%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20The%20world%20should%20be%20glad%20that%20there%20was%20no%20other%20international%20leader%20that%20took%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20Vishwaguru%E2%80%99s%20book%20in%20that%20regard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFast-forward%20about%20two%20thousand%20years%20in%20to%20the%201500s%2C%20Emperor%20Akbar%20is%20another%20Indian%20leader%20that%20achieved%20world%20fame%20for%20his%20deeds.%20To%20focus%20on%20just%20one%20pertinent%20aspect%2C%20he%20took%20secularism%2C%20an%20ideal%20implemented%20already%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Ashoka%2C%20to%20new%20heights%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fsunday-times%2Fdeep-focus%2Fhow-akbar-went-from-great-to-not-so-great%2Farticleshow%2F47402293.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20pro-actively%20encouraging%20tolerance%20of%20all%20faiths%20in%20a%20world%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20was%20already%20ravaged%20by%20religious%20wars.%20From%20India%2C%20he%20set%20a%20bright%20example%20for%20other%20kings%20and%20rulers%20across%20the%20world%20to%20follow%20and%20emulate.%20Our%20current%20dispensation%20can%20certainly%20learn%20a%20lesson%20or%20two%20on%20tolerance%20rather%20than%20literally%20bulldozing%20everyone%20else%20that%20does%20not%20fit%20the%20unabashed%20rightwing%20bill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20to%20the%20modern%20Indian%20nation%20state%2C%20our%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20attained%20Vishwaguru%20status%20in%20the%201950s%20and%20%E2%80%9960s%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FNon-Aligned-Movement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espearheading%20the%20non-aligned%20movement%20in%20a%20world%20that%20was%20reeling%20under%20unprecedented%20devastation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20heaped%20by%20nuclear%20warfare%2C%20holocaust%2C%20world%20war%20II%20and%20the%20Korean%20war.%20He%20collaborated%20with%20other%20world%20leaders%20from%20Egypt%2C%20Yugoslavia%2C%20Ghana%20and%20Indonesia%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20group%20that%20staunchly%20opposed%20expansionist%20wars.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20most%20revisionist%20individuals%20have%20discredited%20Nehru%20for%20his%20non-aligned%20stance%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20embrace%20of%20so-called%20economic%20liberalisation%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20it%20is%20indisputable%20that%20such%20a%20stand%20was%20the%20most%20humanitarian%20one%20to%20take%20for%20continuing%20the%20legacy%20of%20peace%20propagation%20from%20our%20history%20dating%20back%20to%20Buddha%20and%20Ashoka.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cs