%2Farticleshow%2F107147978.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Whither%20Assam%20Muslims%3F%20The%20Story%20of%20Group's%20Exclusion%20from%20Political%2C%20Public%20Spheres%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F21151635%2FScreen-Shot-2021-06-21-at-3.16.21-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20Muslims%20constitute%20one%20of%20the%20most%20marginalised%20social%20groups.%20Besides%20being%20looked%20down%20with%20condescension%20as%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20are%20stereotyped%20as%20%E2%80%9CBangladeshi%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrant%E2%80%9D%20and%20even%20%E2%80%9CJihadi%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20citizenship%20is%20persistently%20under%20attack%2C%20and%20they%20are%20targeted%20through%20the%20state%20power%20through%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%2C%20and%20issues%20such%20as%20eviction%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%20voters%E2%80%9D.%20A%20lot%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20against%20Assam%20Muslims%20are%20already%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20In%20this%20article%2C%20I%20will%20specifically%20deal%20with%20the%20question%20of%20representation%20vis-a-vis%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20of%20Assam%20are%20a%20heterogeneous%20category%2C%20who%20are%20sub-divided%20into%20Miya%20Muslims%2C%20Goriya%2C%20Moria%2C%20Julha%2C%20Deshi%2C%20Bihari%20Muslims%2C%20Muslims%20of%20Barak%20Valley%2C%20etc.%20The%20ruling%20parties%20in%20the%20state%20have%20been%20sharpening%20the%20existing%20faultlines%20amongst%20Muslim%20groups%20in%20the%20state.%20Some%20Muslim%20groups%20like%20Goriya%2C%20Moria%2C%20Julha%2C%20Deshi%2C%20Syed%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20arbitrarily%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20only%20to%20exclude%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%20from%20the%20public%20and%20political%20spheres.%20Miya%20Muslims%20are%20arguably%20the%20most%20discriminated%20and%20excluded%20category%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20in%20this%20article%2C%20I%20will%20briefly%20discuss%20the%20total%20discrimination%20against%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%2C%20in%20general%2C%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20question%20of%20representation%20of%20the%20community%20in%20the%20major%20public%20institutions%2C%20on%20which%20the%20government%20is%20clearly%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdetention-criminalisation-statelessness-the-aftermath-of-assams-nrc%5C%22%3EDetention%2C%20Criminalisation%2C%20Statelessness%3A%20The%20Aftermath%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20NRC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbysmal%20representation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20has%20about%2035%25%20Muslim%20population%2C%20and%20the%20representation%20of%20this%20community%20in%20government%20offices%20is%20abysmally%20low.%20Presently%2C%20there%20are%2016%20ministers%20in%20the%20state%20government%2C%20and%20none%20of%20them%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20state%20has%2034%20districts%20and%20not%20even%20a%20single%20district%20has%20a%20Muslim%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC).%20In%20these%2034%20districts%2C%20not%20even%20a%20single%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fghconline.gov.in%2Findex.php%2Fhonble-the-chief-justice-sitting-judges%2F%5C%22%3EGauhati%20high%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%2023%20judges%2C%20including%20one%20chief%20justice%C2%A0and%20surprisingly%20none%20of%20them%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20These%20discriminations%20are%20not%20only%20limited%20to%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20after%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20state%20has%2031%20Muslim%20MLAs%20out%20of%20126%20MLAs.%20The%20share%20amounts%20to%2024.60%25%20of%20the%20total%20MLAs.%20But%20a%20proportionate%20number%20would%20be%2043%20Muslim%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Assam%20state%20assembly.%20In%20the%202016%20assembly%20elections%2C%2029%20Muslim%20MLAs%20were%20elected%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%2023.02%25%20representation.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%2C%20at%20least%20none%20Muslim%20MLA%20seats%20will%20be%20further%20lost%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20election.%20The%20state%20presently%20has%20two%20Muslim%20MPs%20out%20of%2014%20MPs%2C%20meaning%20only%2014.29%25%20Muslim%20representation%20among%20the%20MPs.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20the%20number%20of%20MPs%2C%20which%20will%20be%20representative%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%20in%20the%20state%2C%20is%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-578102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20has%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhighereducation.assam.gov.in%2Fportlets%2Fprofiles-of-universities-and-colleges%5C%22%3Ecentral%20universities%20and%2014%20state%20universities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20taken%20a%20sample%20of%20five%20universities%20to%20see%20the%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20teaching%20positions%20from%20their%20respective%20website%2C%20in%20these%20universities.%20One%20of%20these%20universities%20is%20a%20central%20university%20(Tezpur%20University)%2C%20and%20the%20other%20four%20are%20state%20universities.%20Out%20of%20the%20four%20state%20universities%2C%20I%20have%20included%20one%20recently%20opened%20university%20(BSSR%20University)%20and%20the%20oldest%20university%20in%20the%20region%20(Gauhati%20University).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETezpur%20Central%20University%20has%20a%20representation%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20of%203.98%25%2C%20while%20Gauhati%20University%20has%20Muslim%20teachers%20of%207.47%25.%20Arabic%20and%20Parsi%20departments%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20University%20alone%20have%20seven%20Muslim%20teachers%2C%20and%20without%20these%20two%20departments%2C%20the%20representation%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20in%20the%20University%20comes%20down%20to%205.54%25.%20Bodoland%20University%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%20(BTR)%20of%20Assam%2C%20does%20not%20have%20a%20single%20Muslim%20teacher%20out%20of%20the%2093%20teachers%20the%20university%20has.%20Another%20relatively%20old%20university%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Dibrugarh%20University%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%201965%2C%20has%20about%202.44%25%20of%20its%20teachers%20Muslim%2C%20which%20is%20abysmally%20low.%20BSSR%20Vishwavidyalaya%20is%20a%20newly%20opened%20university%20in%20the%20Golaghat%20district%20of%20the%20state%20with%205.88%25%20of%20Muslim%20teachers.%20All%20these%20clearly%20show%20severely%20less%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20university%20system%20than%20their%20population%20share%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20is%20about%2035%25.%20Representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20media%20houses%20in%20the%20state%20is%20either%20abysmally%20low%20or%20entirely%20missing.%20This%20underrepresentation%20is%20not%20an%20overnight%20phenomenon%2C%20for%20it%20happened%20over%20the%20decades%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESl.%20No.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EName%20of%20the%20University%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20number%20of%20teachers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20(Permanent%20positions)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPercentage%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E01.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EGauhati%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E361%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E27%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E7.47%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E02.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EBodoland%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E93%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E0%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E0%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E03.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EBSSR%20Vishwavidyalaya%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E17%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E01%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E5.88%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E04.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3ETezpur%20Central%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E276%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E11%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E3.98%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E05.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EDibrugarh%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E286%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E07%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E2.44%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%20Websites%20of%20the%20respective%C2%A0%20university%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0current%20government%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20meant%20for%20the%20poor%20also%20exclude%20Muslims.%20A%20recent%20example%20is%20a%20scheme%2C%20namely%20Mukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Udyamita%20Abhiyaan%20(MMUA)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20scheme%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20to%20improve%20the%20economic%20condition%20of%20rural%20women.%20To%20benefit%20from%20this%20scheme%2C%20women%20cannot%20have%20more%20than%20three%20children%20except%20in%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC).%20Women%20in%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20categories%20can%20benefit%20from%20this%20scheme%20even%20if%20they%20have%20four%20children.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Sachar%20committee%20clarifies%20that%20the%20economic%20condition%20of%20Muslims%20is%20worse%20than%20that%20of%20SCs%20and%20STs.%20And%20in%20a%20time%20when%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20have%20more%20children%2C%20it%20is%20the%20poorest%20sections%20of%20all%20communities%20that%20have%20relatively%20more%20children.%20Mary%20E%20John%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fassam-government-new-schemes-discrimination-communalisation-not-justice-9111255%2F%5C%22%3Ecritiques%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20move%20of%20the%20government%20and%20argues%20that%20this%20scheme%20is%20to%20exclude%20Muslim%20women%20who%20are%20more%20marginalised.%C2%A0%20Another%20scheme%2C%20namely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-chief-minister-is-communalising-land-settlement-scheme-aiudf%2Farticle66144465.ece%5C%22%3EVasundhara%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20through%20which%20land%20rights%20are%20given%20to%20landless%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%20too%20excludes%20Muslims%20totally.%20There%20are%20many%20such%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Overwhelming%20number%20of%20Muslims%20as%20undertrials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20jails%20of%20the%20state%20throws%20a%20very%20interesting%20picture.%20As%20per%20Prison%20Statistics%20India%202022%2C%20published%20by%20the%20National%20Crimes%20Record%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%2055.6%25%20of%20convicts%20lodged%20in%20the%20prisons%20of%20Assam%20are%20Muslims.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20undertrials%20lodged%20in%20the%20jails%2C%2052.54%25%20of%20them%20are%20Muslims%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20above%20discussion%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20discrimination%20and%20exclusion%20are%20visible%20in%20Assam.%20Muslims%20in%20Assam%20are%20excluded%20from%20decision-making%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20various%20institutions%2C%20including%20institutions%20of%20higher%20learning%20and%20administration.%20They%20are%20purposely%20and%20systematically%20made%20voiceless%20regarding%20policy%20formation%20and%20problem-raising.%20An%20exhaustive%20study%20to%20understand%20the%20discrimination%20and%20underrepresentation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20public%20life%20in%20the%20state%20is%20the%20urgent%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20The%20situation%20is%20all%20the%20more%20alarming%20as%20Abdur%20Rahman%20writes%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EAbsent%20in%20Politics%20and%20Power%2C%20Political%20Exclusion%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20openly%20portrays%20itself%20as%20anti-Muslim%20and%20has%20been%20against%20all%20forms%20of%20their%20empowerment.%20By%20depriving%20them%20of%20a%20just%20and%20equitable%20share%20in%20education%2C%20economy%20and%20politics%2C%20the%20party%20intends%20to%20push%20them%20into%20becoming%20second%20class%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20(p.97).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20word%20discrimination%20is%20meaningless%20if%20the%20discrimination%20against%20Muslims%20is%20not%20considered.%20While%20other%20discriminated%20social%20groups%20enjoy%20the%20benefit%20of%20reservation%2C%20most%20of%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%2C%20especially%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%20of%20the%20state%2C%20do%20not%20have%20any%20reservation%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20system.%20They%20are%20always%20pushed%20to%20the%20margin%20to%20struggle%20for%20basic%20survival%20%E2%80%93%20food%2C%20clothes%2C%20and%20land.%20The%20picture%20of%20missing%20Muslims%20from%20public%20institutions%20is%20completely%20contradictory%20to%20the%20claim%2C%20%3Cem%3Esabke%20saath%20sabka%20bikas%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20a%20community%20away%20from%20the%20positions%20of%20power%20in%20government-run%20institutions%20leads%20to%20stereotyping%20of%20the%20community.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20to%20bring%20Muslims%20of%20Assam%20into%20a%20suitable%20reservation%20system%20in%20the%20line%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20to%20ensure%20proportionate%20representation%20of%20this%20community%20in%20the%20social%2C%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20educational%20positions%20and%20to%20ensure%20social%20justice%20to%20this%20marginalised%20community.%20The%20constitution%20of%20India%20promised%20equal%20opportunity%20for%20all%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20citizens%2C%20and%20it%20is%20time%20to%20deliver%20this%20promise%20to%20these%20marginalised%20citizens%20of%20peripheral%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENazimuddin%20Siddique%20teaches%20Sociology%20at%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20can%20be%20contacted%20at%20sid.nazimuddin%40gmail.com.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706183199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F21151635%2FScreen-Shot-2021-06-21-at-3.16.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muslims%2C%20who%20constitute%2035%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20are%20abysmally%20represented%20in%20the%20positions%20of%20power.%20Their%20share%2C%20however%2C%20among%20the%20undertrials%20in%20the%20state%20in%2052.54%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Claudia%20Schiffer's%20cat%20steals%20the%20show%20at%20Argylle%20premiere%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706182692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F14B10%2Fproduction%2F_132425748_cr6c7cb153871aa1c7a21d31b82f05779efb08ddf1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68091914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20model's%20cat%20Chip%20got%20all%20the%20media%20attention%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20new%20spy%20comedy%20Argylle%20in%20London.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A117%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68091914%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68091914.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68091914.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Bloc%20In%20Pieces%3F%20Amid%20Turmoil%2C%20Architect%20Nitish%20Kumar%20On%20Way%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20is%20yet%20to%20enter%20the%20election%20amphitheatre%2C%20but%20is%20already%20out%20on%20a%20limb%20after%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20Punjab%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%20decided%20against%20fighting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20join%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20when%20the%20marching%20group%20enters%20Bihar%20on%20January%2030%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20decision%20to%20not%20walk%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20whose%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20or%20JD(U)%2C%20which%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20in%20the%20ruling%20Bihar%20government%2C%20has%20given%20a%20subtle%20message%20that%20all%20is%20not%20well%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20was%20one%20of%20the%20architects%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20could%20be%20struggling%20with%20internal%20turmoil%20is%20also%20reinforced%20by%20allegations%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20RJD%20chief%20over%20%26quot%3Bdynastic%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20charge%20that%20JD(U)%20leader%20KC%20Tyagi%20today%20refuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNitish%20Kumar%20was%20addressing%20a%20programme%20organised%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Karpoori%20Thakur%2C%20whom%20he%20has%20idolised.%20Like%20all%20great%20socialists%2C%20Thakur%20abhorred%20dynastic%20succession%20in%20politics.%20This%20was%20the%20simple%20fact%20Nitish%20Kumar%20wanted%20to%20underscore.%20Nothing%20more%20should%20be%20read%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tyagi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNitish%20Kumar%20has%20no%20wish%20to%20condemn%20any%20regional%20party%20or%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tyagi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20think%20a%20dynasty%20is%20essential%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20are%20free%20to%20draw%20their%20own%20conclusion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20today%20asked%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20meet%20him%20in%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20pacify%20the%20alliance%20partner%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav's%20younger%20son%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20had%20taken%20over%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20when%20Mr%20Kumar%20broke%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202022%2C%20and%20rejoined%20the%20Grand%20Alliance%20(Mahagathbandhan)%2C%20whose%20members%20include%20the%20Congress%20and%20three%20Left%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20has%20already%20made%20it%20clear%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20will%20fight%20the%20election%20solo.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20blamed%20Bengal%20Congress%20chief%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20as%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20breakdown%20of%20alliance%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%20The%20Trinamool%20has%20alleged%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20is%20working%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20sabotage%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20Punjab%20has%20also%20declined%20to%20share%20seats%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20northern%20border%20state.%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20said%20the%20AAP%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20general%20election%20due%20in%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706182680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F85q53olg_nitish-kumar-rahul-gandhi_625x300_25_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-in-pieces-amid-turmoil-architect-nitish-kumar-on-way-out-4930018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20young%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20is%20yet%20to%20enter%20the%20election%20amphitheatre%2C%20but%20is%20already%20out%20on%20a%20limb%20after%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20Punjab%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%20decided%20against%20fighting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-in-pieces-amid-turmoil-architect-nitish-kumar-on-way-out-4930018%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-in-pieces-amid-turmoil-architect-nitish-kumar-on-way-out-4930018%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-in-pieces-amid-turmoil-architect-nitish-kumar-on-way-out-4930018%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharat%20Ratna%20To%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20As%20Impetus%20For%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20U-Turn%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20will%20exit%20the%20state's%20ruling%20%3Cem%3EMahagathbandhan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%2C%20by%20extension%20the%20now-stuttering%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20and%20re-ally%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20ahead%20of%20the%20April%2FMay%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20a%20fifth%20U-turn%20by%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20boss%20-%20who%20has%20flip-flopped%20between%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%2For%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20since%202013%20-%20has%20triggered%20speculation%20over%20what%20led%20to%20the%20latest%20jump.%20At%20(or%20near)%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20of%20probable%20causes%20is%20the%20BJP's%20decision%20to%20award%20two-time%20former%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20-%20India's%20highest%20civilian%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%20was%20an%20iconic%20socialist%20leader%20who%20was%20Chief%20Minister%20twice%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20and%20is%20credited%20with%20implementing%20the%20state's%20contentious%20alcohol%20prohibition%20policy.%20Still%20remembered%20today%20as%20'jan%20nayak'%2C%20or%20'leader%20of%20the%20people'%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakur's%20legacy%20remains%20a%20valuable%20asset%20for%20political%20parties%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20Nitish%20Kumar%20(and%20Lalu%20Yadav's)%20mentor%2C%20and%20both%20had%20strongly%20advocated%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20award%20was%20confirmed%20-%20Mr%20Modi%20did%20so%20on%20X%20and%20hailed%20Mr%20Thakur%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20champion%20for%20the%20marginalised%20and%20a%20stalwart%20of%20equality%20and%20empowerment%26quot%3B%20-%20Nitish%20Kumar%20thanked%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Significantly%2C%20he%20also%20took%20a%20potshot%20at%20the%20Congress%3B%20he%20said%20he%20had%20petitioned%20every%20central%20government%20since%202007%20(when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power)%20and%20it%20was%20only%20the%20Modi%20government%20that%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706181420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fi0ef5a8k_nitish-kumar-karpoori-thakur_625x300_24_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-news-bharat-ratna-to-karpoori-thakur-as-impetus-for-nitish-kumars-bjp-u-turn-4929898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20will%20exit%20the%20state's%20ruling%20Mahagathbandhan%20and%2C%20by%20extension%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20and%20re-ally%20with%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20ahead%20of%20the%20April%2FMay%20Lok%20Election%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-news-bharat-ratna-to-karpoori-thakur-as-impetus-for-nitish-kumars-bjp-u-turn-4929898%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-news-bharat-ratna-to-karpoori-thakur-as-impetus-for-nitish-kumars-bjp-u-turn-4929898%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-news-bharat-ratna-to-karpoori-thakur-as-impetus-for-nitish-kumars-bjp-u-turn-4929898%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ladakh%3A%20Renaming%20Govt%20Health%20Centres%20'Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandirs'%20Invites%20Backlash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163733%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-25-at-2.06.02-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20rename%20the%20health%20centres%20as%20%E2%80%9CAyushman%20Arogya%20Mandirs%E2%80%9D%20has%20stirred%20a%20fierce%20controversy%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20with%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20most%20influential%20Buddhist%20organisation%20and%20elected%20representatives%20calling%20this%20an%20affront%20to%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20living%20in%20the%20two-district%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecision%2C%20controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%20decided%20to%20rename%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat-%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Wellness%20Centres%20(AB-HWCs)%20as%20%E2%80%98Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandirs%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20tag%20line%20%E2%80%98Arogyam%20Parmam%20Dhanam%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20wrote%20to%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20November%2025%2C%202023%20to%20implement%20the%20rebranding%20exercise%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20submit%20photographs%20of%20these%20health%20facilities%20with%20the%20new%20title%20by%20December%2031%2C%202023.%20It%20even%20earmarked%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20facility%20for%20this%20rebranding%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20decision%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20especially%20in%20Buddhist-majority%20Leh%20district%2C%20where%20a%20prominent%20religious%20group%20has%20taken%20strong%20objection%20to%20it%20and%20written%20to%20the%20elected%20bodies%20of%20the%20region%20to%20raise%20their%20concerns%20with%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20over%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20recent%20order%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20renaming%20the%20Govt.%20medical%20aid%20centers%2F%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%20centers%20as%20%E2%80%9CAyushman%20Arogya%20Mandir%E2%80%99%20is%20unfortunate%20and%20tantamount%20to%20playing%20with%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chering%20Dorjey%20Lakrook%2C%20acting%20president%2C%20Ladakh%20Buddhist%20Association%20(LBA)%20wrote%20to%20the%20chief%20executive%20councilors%20of%20the%20Hill%20Councils%20of%20both%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LBA%20has%20asked%20heads%20of%20both%20the%20elected%20bodies%20to%20get%20the%20decision%20rescinded.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20secular%20country%20and%20using%20religious%20names%20and%20symbols%20in%20government%20departments%20is%20unconstitutional%20and%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dorjay%20said%2C%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dorjay%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Democratic%20Party-BJP%20government%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20said%20that%20this%20decision%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20us.%20What%20is%20the%20fun%20of%20naming%20hospitals%20as%20mandirs%3F%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20steps%20towards%20making%20India%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LBA%20is%20the%20most%20powerful%20religious%20group%20in%20Buddhist-dominated%20Leh%20and%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20guardian%20of%20Buddhist%20identity%20in%20the%20region.%20It%20has%20considerable%20influence%20on%20social%20and%20political%20matters%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694390%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERebranded%20health%20centres%20in%20Ladakh.%20Photos%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rechristening%20of%20health%20centres%20has%20also%20evoked%20criticism%20from%20elected%20representatives%20of%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20councillors%20of%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Development%20Council-Leh%20have%20written%20to%20the%20CECs%20of%20both%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20that%20people%E2%80%99s%20sentiments%20have%20been%20hurt%20by%20the%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20decision%20might%20become%20a%20hindrance%20to%20health%20centres%20being%20universally%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20letter%20signed%20by%2010%20councilors%20of%20the%20Hill%20Council%2C%20Leh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20religious%20and%20cultural%20sentiments%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20they%20have%20also%20urged%20the%20CECs%20to%20get%20the%20decision%20repealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmanla%20Dorje%20Nurboo%2C%20councilor%20Saspol%20constituency%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20people%20are%20offended%20by%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20health%20facilities%20should%20be%20accessible%20to%20everyone%20but%20this%20move%20will%20create%20hindrances%20in%20accessing%20these%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Smanla%2C%20who%20is%20also%20president%20of%20Youth%20Congress%20in%20Ladakh%20UT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20blames%20local%20authorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20damage-control%20exercise%2C%20CEC%2C%20LAHDC-Leh%2C%20Tashi%20Gaylson%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20written%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20B.D.%20Mishra%20to%20express%20his%20concern%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20said%2C%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20that%20the%20move%20has%20generated%20significant%20resentment%20among%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%2C%20however%2C%20put%20the%20blame%20on%20officials%20from%20the%20Ladakh%20health%20department%20for%20the%20controversy%2C%20saying%20they%20could%20have%20translated%20the%20title%20into%20the%20state%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20handout%2C%20the%20CEC%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CGoI%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20offend%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20sentiments%20as%20the%20order%20clearly%20stipulated%20that%20the%20full%20and%20exact%20title%20could%20be%20translated%20into%20the%20state%20language%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20health%20department%20overlooked%20the%20directive%20and%20opted%20for%20the%20easiest%20path%20without%20considering%20the%20potential%20negative%20impact%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20has%20erupted%20at%20a%20time%20when%20two%20prominent%20groups%20of%20Ladakh%20are%20involved%20in%20parleys%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20seek%20safeguards%20for%20the%20region%20after%20its%20detachment%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Leh%20Apex%20Body%20and%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20two%20conglomerates%20seeking%20safeguards%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20last%20month%20met%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20Nitayanad%20Rai%20to%20discuss%20the%20concerns%20and%20issues%20emerging%2