y%20important%20impact%20on%20our%20students.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20perseverance%20for%20him%20to%20open%20a%20restaurant%2C%20make%20a%20film%20in%20China%20as%20a%20foreigner%2C%20and%20succeed.%20His%20success%20story%20inspires%20young%20children%20to%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams%2C%20defy%20difficulties%20and%20keep%20working%20hard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dev%E2%80%99s%20inspiration%20journey%20is%20taught%20in%20the%20schools%20of%20China%20today.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338749%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDev%E2%80%99s%20inspirational%20journey%20is%20taught%20in%20the%20schools%20of%20China%20today.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDev%20also%20demonstrated%20the%20importance%20of%20cross-cultural%20communication.%20He%20not%20only%20brought%20Indian%20food%20culture%20to%20China%20but%20also%20spread%20Chinese%20culture%20to%20India%20through%20films%20and%20other%20means.%20This%20kind%20of%20cross-cultural%20exchange%20helps%20to%20improve%20the%20und