d%20ka%20business%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(scrap%20business).%20It%20was%20my%20passion%20towards%20nature%20conservation%20that%20kept%20me%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20feels%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20manage%20waste%20but%20ours%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20concept%20of%20giving%20away%20rewards%20comes%20from%20my%20basic%20understanding%20of%20human%20nature.%20We%20all%20love%20free%20stuff%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%3F%20So%20the%20reward%20system%20has%20worked%20perfectly%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20his%20company%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20we%20have%20an%20app%20which%20a%20consumer%20downloads.%20They%20segregate%20their%20waste%20and%20schedule%20a%20visit%20from%20the%20app.%20Our%20collection%20executive%20comes%20and%20picks%20up%20their%20waste.%20The%20consumer%20can%20go%20to%20the%20application%20and%20collect%20their%20reward%20points.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20products%20that%20consumers%20can%20buy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20usually%20have%20household%20stuff%20and%20groceries%20which%20the%20consumers%20can%20buy%20for%20free.%20We%20deliver%20them%20to%20their%20homes%20within%2072%20hours%20without%20a%20delivery%20charge.%20So%20basically%2C%20you%20get%20something%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20limit%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311633%2Fruhani-verma-built-indias-first-carbon-negative-recyclable-public-toilet-amritsar-airport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamount%20of%20waste%20%3C%2Fa%3Eyou%20need%20to%20be%20picked%20up%2C%20and%20the%20rewards%20are%20based%20on%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20waste%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20waste%20is%20collected%2C%