-for-10000-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattitude%20towards%20school%3C%2Fa%3E.%20From%20a%20boy%20who%20sat%20quietly%20and%20waited%20for%20the%20bell%20to%20go%20off%20so%20he%20could%20rush%20home%2C%20to%20one%20of%20the%20star%20students%20of%20his%20class%20whose%20hand%20went%20up%20every%20time%20a%20question%20was%20asked%2C%20the%20transformation%20was%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmol%20is%20one%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20children%20around%20the%20world%20who%20have%20been%20positively%20impacted%20by%20the%20growing%20digital%20revolution.%20And%20exacerbating%20this%20are%20organisations%20such%20as%20Global%20Digital%20Alliance%20(GDA)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20global%20movement%20of%20leaders%20to%20prioritise%20digital%20inclusion%20in%20education%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Muskaan%20Dreams%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tech-driven%20non-profit%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20GDA%20brings%20together%20stakeholders%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20work%20in%20collaboration%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335433%2Fnorthstar-school-rajkot-sustainable-design-santiniketan-open-learning-ib-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebridge%20the%20digital%20divide%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%2C%20Muskaan%20Dreams%20is%20championing%20change%20through%20a%20two-pronged%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20wherein%20they%20bring%20tech%20and%20innovation%20into%20public%20schools%20in%20India%20and%20empower%20teachers%20to%20become%20adept%20at%20this%20new%20wave%20of%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20strongly%20believe%20that%20digital%20access%20is%20a%20necessity%20rather%20than%20a%20luxury.%20And%20this%20is%20exactly%20the%20message%20the%20Global%20Digital%20Alliance%20is%20attempting%20to%20drive%20home%20by%20mobilising%20technology%20to%20create%20educational%20equality%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%