0the%20largest%20populations%20and%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20a%20quadriplegic%20or%20a%20paraplegic%20person%20to%20live%20with%20dignity.%20There%20was%20no%20one%20to%20take%20care%20of%20me%20when%20my%20mom%20got%20sick%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20started%20researching%20and%20found%20that%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20long-term%20rehabilitation%20centres%20or%20places%20that%20offered%20care%20for%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries.%20Her%20mother%20then%20persuaded%20her%20to%20start%20such%20a%20haven%20that%20provides%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20for%20people%20with%20severe%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20laughed%20off%20the%20idea%20as%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20about%20running%20or%20financing%20a%20non-profit%20organisation.%20But%20the%20death%20of%20these%20girls%20made%20me%20wake%20up.%20If%20I%20am%20just%20going%20to%20be%20afraid%20to%20do%20something%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%20No%20one%20understands%20this%20better%20than%20me%20due%20to%20my%20lived%20experience.%20I%20decided%20to%20raise%20my%20voice%20and%20do%20whatever%20I%20can%20to%20somehow%20uplift%20this%20segment%20of%20society%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20so%20completely%20invisible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20she%20started%20Soulfree%20Inspire.%20People%20come%20with%20a%20caregiver%20and%20spend%20about%206%20months%20in%20the%20centre.%20They%20receive%20training%2C%20which%20Preethi%20calls%20re-engineering%2C%20where%20they%20get%20emotional%20and%20physical%20rehabilitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20restore%20their%20will%20to%20live.%20Our%20aim%20is%20to%20restore%20self-reliance%20from%20a%20physiological%2C%20psychological%20and%20socio%20economic%20perspective.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20them%20to%20go%20home%20and%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20some%20money.%20We%20are%20giving%20international%20s